p:
Chemical composition. Essential oil (
 trans-anethole as the main compound) (
 Orav et al., 2008); chlorogenic acid derivatives; flavonoids (orientin, vitexin, and others, coumarin derivatives; triterpenes and steroidal compounds (
 Zobel et al., 1991; 
 Reichling and Galati, 2004; 
 Abdollahi Fard, 2012).
